Date: Thu, 9 Jul 2026 14:59:39 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 20/20] web-app: full-screen big dialogs on mobile viewports

Add a fullscreenOnMobile prop to <Dialog>/<DialogWithHeader> that, below
the $dialog-breakpoint (500px), expands the dialog to fill the viewport:
no rounded corners, margin, shadow or top padding, so it goes edge to
edge on phones. Opt the big dialogs into it: settings, about, gallery
(media view), contact and group profiles, the new-chat family (create
chat, clone, create group, create broadcast) and the QR scanner.
Onboarding dialogs are intentionally left unchanged for now.
